    "description_long": "This is a blue convertible car with a streamlined, sporty design and a soft top roof. The body features smooth, aerodynamic lines, with a slightly raised rear and a sloping hood. The car has two doors, alloy wheels, and side mirrors that match the body color. The windshield and windows are tinted, and the headlights are sleek and integrated into the front fascia. The rear of the car is simple, with rectangular taillights and a subtle trunk outline. The overall appearance suggests a compact, urban-friendly vehicle designed for both style and performance.",
